title: Taliyah E Bug?
body: When Quinn e's to Taliyah, Taliyah can throw her E and one hit Quinn after she has landed with none of the boulders being exploded.

replies.body:
The best place to post bug reports is the Report a Bug sub-boards on NA. This way, the appropriate team(s) can track the issues more efficiently.

http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report

Thanks!
